'''大卫·古德威利'''（{{lang-en|'''David Goodwillie'''}}，{{bd|1989年|3月28日|catIdx=Goodwillie, David}}）出生於[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]中部[[英國的指定市|指定市]][[史特靈|史特靈]]，是一名[[英式足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力[[蘇格蘭足球乙級聯賽|蘇格蘭足球乙級聯賽]]球會[[克莱德足球俱乐部|克莱德]]。

==生平==
===球會===
;登地聯
葛維尼在家鄉參加當地的青年球隊，於2003年在[[邓迪|邓迪]]參加「蘇格蘭青年足球協會」（Scottish Youth FA）的試訓賽時被[[邓迪联足球俱乐部|登地聯]]相中，以14歲之齡獲邀加盟。他於2005年3月與球會簽署首份[[職業|職業]]合約，同年12月31日葛維尼首次為一隊上陣，在作客[[埃布羅克斯球場|埃布羅克斯]]0-3負於[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]的賽事末段後補登場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/4569378.stm |title=Rangers 3-0 Dundee United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-12-31 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg3yzp5A?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/4569378.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。翌年3月4日作客對[[希伯尼安足球俱乐部|喜百年]]，葛維尼第5次後補上陣，於完場前射入個人首個入球兼為球隊打破光蛋負1-3<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/4769012.stm |title=Hibernian 3-1 Dundee United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-03-04 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg3zl3aP?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/4769012.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[2005年至2006年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2005/06年球季]]葛維尼合共為一隊後補上陣10場，但絕大部分僅有數分鐘亮相時間，整體上陣時間還不足90分鐘<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=42894&seasonid=135 |title=David Goodwillie |publisher=''Soccerbase'' |accessdate=2008-11-11 }}{{Dead link|date=2019年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref></small>。

2006年10月23日葛維尼與球會續簽三年半新約直到2010年夏季才屆滿<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11794_2393632,00.html |title=Thompson backs Brewster |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2006-10-23 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310092117/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11794_2393632,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，數天後獲派首次正選上陣作客對[[法尔科克足球俱乐部|福爾柯克]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6089770.stm |title=Falkirk 5-1 Dundee United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-28 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg423Ky6?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/6089770.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，卻以1-5大敗而回，成為時任球員兼領隊的[[克雷格·布雷斯特|克雷格·布雷斯特]]下台導火線。由於球隊前線傷兵問題嚴重，葛維尼在新任領隊[[奇治·尼雲|奇治·尼雲]]（Craig Levein）麾下，於上半季餘下的兩個月再取得兩次正選上陣機會<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/6206391.stm |title=Levein bemoaning injury to Hunt |date=2006-12-23 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2008-11-11 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg44Cn4w?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/6206391.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但隨著1月份[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]引入新球員後，他在下季只能呆坐後備席，於新年後僅獲派6次上陣。

在[[2007年至2008年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]季初為登地聯後補上陣兩次後，於11月2日葛維尼被外借到[[蘇格蘭足球乙級聯賽|蘇乙]]球會[[拉夫流浪足球會|拉夫流浪]]兩個月<small><ref name="loan">{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/r/raith_rovers/7075683.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-02 |title=Goodwillie on loan to Raith Rovers |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2012-04-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67IXVJMty?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/r/raith_rovers/7075683.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後獲延長借用至球季結束，期間上陣14場聯賽及射入6球，協助球隊獲得聯賽季軍及取得升班附加賽資格，但於準決賽兩回合累計2-4不敵[[艾迪爾聯足球會|艾迪爾聯]]出局<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_div_1/7379022.stm |title=Airdrie 2-2 Raith Rovers (4-2) |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-03 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016213440/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_div_1/7379022.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

新球季季初葛維尼獲派在[[蘇格蘭聯賽盃|蘇格蘭聯賽盃]]首兩輪的賽事上陣，在較低級別的球隊身上取得3個入球。2009年1月17日葛維尼再續約多1年至2012年5月才屆滿<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4805556,00.html |title=Four more Tangerines sign up |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-01-17 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310080514/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_4805556,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。[[2008年至2009年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]他在季末階段於[[蘇超|蘇超]]再次取得入球，先在2009年4月4日主場對[[希伯尼安足球俱乐部|喜百年]]於完場前為球隊扳平2-2；5月2日作客再戰喜百年，葛維尼再次於完場前入球，這次以2-1絕殺對手<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8028078.stm |title=Hibernian 1-2 Dundee United |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-02 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307175701/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8028078.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。葛維尼在蘇超的首3個入球全部在喜百年身上取得，並且全部在完場前射入，獲得勝和負各一的成績。

[[2009年至2010年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]]葛維尼開始成為一隊常規正選，在開季後首5場賽事射入3球，直到季末合共轟入12球，成為球隊次席射手，其表現獲得確認，於2010年4月19日獲選「[[2009年至2010年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽#年度最佳|蘇超最佳青年球員]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8631202.stm |title=Dundee Utd striker Goodwillie nets young player award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-04-19 |accessdate=2010-04-21 |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CIe3JBce?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/scot_prem/8631202.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

[[2010年至2011年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2010/11年球季]]葛維尼繼續表現出色，上半季已射入11球，[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]於冬季[[轉會窗|轉會窗]]口頭出價，但金額僅為登地聯估值150萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的一半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/9344056.stm |title=Dundee United reject Rangers offer for David Goodwillie |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-01-07 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226142813/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/dundee_utd/9344056.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年3月31日葛維尼與登地聯延長一年合約，留隊直至2013年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/12927661.stm |title=David Goodwillie extends Dundee United stay |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-31 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110405063435/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/12927661.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月1日葛維尼獲選為[[蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員|蘇格蘭PFA年度最佳青年球員]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13256109.stm |title=Emilio Izaguirre wins Scotland's players' player prize |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-01 |accessdate=2011-05-02 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69mmLBwSx?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13256109 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後再下一城，當選[[蘇格蘭FWA年度最佳青年球員|蘇格蘭FWA年度最佳青年球員]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13406778.stm |title=More awards for Izaguirre, Goodwillie and Paatelainen |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-15 |accessdate=2011-05-17 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg4HXIes?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13406778 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

球季結束後多支球隊追逐葛維尼，[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]率先發難，但仍未達到登地聯提高估值的200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13854851.stm |title=Dundee United receive two offers for David Goodwillie |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-24 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626113009/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13854851.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[黑池足球會|黑池]]其後出價160萬英鎊仍然被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14286377.stm |title=Dundee United reject new bid for David Goodwillie |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-27 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110820123226/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14286377.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，葛維尼表示希望南下[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]參賽<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14322861.stm |title=United stirker Goodwillie eyes England move - Houston |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-28 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110804001948/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14322861.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]與格拉斯哥流浪相繼加入競爭，布力般流浪首先出價180英鎊被拒<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_7067349,00.html |title=Rovers rejected over Goodwillie |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-07-29 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg4KCBtd?url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_7067349,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14344646.stm |title=Rangers remain in the hunt for striker David Goodwille |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-29 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110808195524/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14344646.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[2011年至2012年蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|2011/12年球季]]展開，葛維尼沒有在登地聯的揭幕戰作客1-0擊敗[[哈茨足球俱乐部|赫斯]]上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14321355.stm |title=Hearts 0-1 Dundee Utd |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-31 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110804001931/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14321355.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，登地聯證實接納布力般流浪總值280萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的出價，正讓葛維尼與布力般流浪商討私人條件<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,,11676_7074206,00.html |title=Rovers agree Goodwillie fee |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-07-31 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg4LLe5V?url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,,11676_7074206,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;布力般流浪
雖然大局已定，但[[流浪者足球俱乐部|格拉斯哥流浪]]仍然盡最後努力，於葛維尼簽約前多番出價，惟登地聯以條件未及布力般流浪予以拒絕，葛維尼最終於2011年8月3日加盟布力般流浪，簽約四年，轉會費詳情沒有透露，據報初步為200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，另加80萬英鎊附加條款<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14344125.stm |title=Blackburn Rovers sign David Goodwillie from Dundee United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-03 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110901183217/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14344125.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
葛維尼曾代表蘇格蘭在各個年齡級別參加國際賽，年僅15歲已代表蘇格蘭U16上陣，現時是[[蘇格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|U21]]成員，於2008年11月18日對[[北愛爾蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|北愛爾蘭]]首次後補上陣<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/international_fixture_details.cfm?page=105&matchID=82155 |title=SCOTLAND v NORTHERN IRELAND |publisher=[[蘇格蘭足球協會|''scottishfa.co.uk'']] |date= |accessdate=2010-04-21}}</ref></small>。他於2010年11月獲首次徵召加入[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|大國腳]]行列，備戰對[[法羅群島國家足球隊|法羅群島]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]，他在該場賽事下半場獲派後補首次上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/scotland/9187834.stm |title=Scotland 3–0 Faroe Islands |accessdate=2011-02-11 |date=2010-11-16 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |archive-date=2017-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906000538/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/scotland/9187834.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但他的大國腳生涯卻因其[[强奸|强奸]]案件而一度受阻<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14285066.stm |title=Goodwillie in Scotland plans after rape charge dropped |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-25 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110804002009/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14285066.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於2011年8月才再獲徵召入伍備戰對[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/14360419.stm |title=David Goodwillie selected for Scotland duty |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-02 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2011-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919205340/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/14360419.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===私人生活===
2008年5月27日葛維尼在夜總會因維護朋友引發的打鬥傷人，其後同意接受250[[英鎊|英鎊]]定額罰款<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://thescotsman.scotsman.com/scotland/Footballer-fined-after-punching-man.4229128.jp |title=Footballer fined after punching man in nightclub |date=2008-06-27 |publisher=''The Scotsman'' |accessdate=2008-06-30 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Bg9I2j1A?url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/footballer-fined-after-punching-man-in-nightclub-1-1077712 |archive-date=2012-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>。葛維尼在2009年9月20日再發生類似事故，於一名夜總會門衛頭部被擊中昏迷後被拘留，而兩天後球隊在[[蘇格蘭聯賽盃|蘇格蘭聯賽盃]]迎戰[[罗斯郡足球俱乐部|羅斯郡]]，即他亦同時違反球隊在賽前72小時的宵禁規條<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.eveningtelegraph.co.uk/output/2009/09/21/story13822181t0.shtm |title=Goodwillie in hot water |publisher=Evening Telegraph |date=2009-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090925001302/http://www.eveningtelegraph.co.uk/output/2009/09/21/story13822181t0.shtm |archivedate=2009-09-25 |accessdate=2010-04-21 }}</ref></small>，兩個月後被法庭罰款200[[英鎊|英鎊]]了事<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.thesun.co.uk/scotsol/homepage/news/2723771/Dundee-United-star-guilty-of-assault.html |title=I KO'd rugby giant butt he started it |publisher=''thesun.co.uk'' |date=2009-11-11 |accessdate=2009-11-11 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023145511/http://www.thesun.co.uk/scotsol/homepage/news/2723771/Dundee-United-star-guilty-of-assault.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2011年1月17日葛維尼被控於一個[[新年|新年]]派對[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]一名24歲女子<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-12209157 |title=Dundee United's David Goodwillie charged over rape |publisher=[[BBC|''BBC News'']] |date=2011-01-17 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301142937/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-12209157 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終因證據不足獲撤銷控罪<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-tayside-central-14279600 |title=David Goodwillie rape charge dropped |publisher=[[BBC|''BBC News'']] |date=2011-07-25 |accessdate=2011-08-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112023530/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-scotland-tayside-central-14279600 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

